metadata.name: Retrogradica
metadata.description:
“Ma’am, do you know what happened here tonight?”

She looked the man straight in the eyes and sobbed.

“Yes, in fact I do know what happened here tonight. I 
remember it so vividly.”

The man kneeled down to the weeping woman.

“I know this must be hard for you, but I need you to tell 
me.” 

She wiped her tears away and a malevolent smile crept 
onto her face.

“I fired the shots, and I enjoyed doing so.”

(2560 x 2560)
